/// Runs multiple futures with epoch awareness, waiting for all to complete.
///
/// # Epoch Semantics
///
/// All futures share the same epoch context. If the epoch expires or transitions
/// before all futures complete, the behavior depends on the policy:
///
/// - `AbortAll`: Returns epoch error immediately
/// - `DrainExecuting`: Waits for in-progress futures, prevents new polls
/// - `Fail`: Returns epoch error
